text: Mia Khalifa (born 1993) is a Lebanese-American social media personality and former pornographic movie actress and webcam model., She is best known for her career as a pornographic actress from 2014 to 2015. On December 28, 2014, Pornhub revealed that she was the No. 1 ranked performer on their website. ==Early life== Raised as a devout Christian Catholic in what she describes as a "very conservative" home, Khalifa moved with her family to the United States around the year 2000 or 2001. == References == ==Other websites== * * * * Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:American pornographic actors Category:Actors from Miami Category:People from Beirut Category:Sports commentators
